      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presented in museum-grade condition, this 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo features the legendary 2JZ-GTE inline-six power plant, retaining its factory sequential twin-turbocharger configuration and unmodified ECU. Power is delivered through the robust Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission to a Torsen limited-slip differential. The chassis remains perfectly balanced with original double-wishbone suspension components and factory-spec forged alloy wheels. Meticulously maintained, the engine bay is clinically clean, showing no signs of heat cycling on the wiring harness or vacuum lines. This example boasts all original VIN tags on every panel, confirming its accident-free history and structural integrity. A truly turn-key investment for the discerning collector seeking peak JDM performance and mechanical purity.",
