      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defines the term 'mint condition.' This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen a drop of rain. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with a professional ceramic coating, free of any chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no signs of wear, and the original protective films are still present on several interior trim pieces. Mechanically, it is flawless, having followed a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule at certified dealerships\u2014all service records are included. Every button, sensor, and feature functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to own a collector-grade example that looks, smells, and drives like new.",
